{"tid":144218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗米華、向太、楊受成都撐七警！","createTime":"2017-03-05T08:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T01:29:42.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d943b1fbadd5f4bdc0401c054551a0298b94cc18","tid":144218,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"七警案審結後，全部被告罪成並被判入獄2年，引起社會爭議，其後有建制派人士上周籌組「敬言仁基金」，用以協助處理雨傘運動而受影響的警務人員及其家屬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐款人包括向華強、楊受成、外號「洗米華」的周焯華等。不過他們未有出席捐款交贈支票儀式，只有向太陳嵐作為代表到場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐款人/機構\t金額<br />\n太陽城娛樂公司周焯華\t$1,000,000<br />\n中國星娛樂集團向華強\t$1,000,000<br />\n英皇娛樂集團楊受成\t$500,000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">江湖猛人幾時咁支持警察架？</span>"},{"pid":"fc379553aabf5709e25d97168a1f79916b5615ca","tid":144218,"uid":9120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"不用分得那麼細嘛"},{"pid":"9f1cff64a7c4eb789e8752cc8f7a781373ca0120","tid":144218,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17376ae3eb378ec372dcdc7d8c1407c035e4a5c","tid":144218,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"新技安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0755d0ae8372b64cd9cfa6f35db6062771f32d","tid":144218,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新技安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警、賊，行得咁埋，真係前所未見"},{"pid":"5ad32cb8eb64c9e689b0911e8f9bcb984dd5fc2f","tid":144218,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"六十年代收皮既你地識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836d6a8b5dd7baed98b109258e07fc84b8f0657d","tid":144218,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"【A1頭條】江湖救七 <span style=\"color: red;\">向太洗米華楊受成籌安家費$7,777,777撐七警</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向華強父親向前為三合會組織新義安創辦人<br />\n<br />\n外號「洗米華」的周焯華則是澳門江湖猛人，是「崩牙駒」尹國駒徒孫，發跡前曾在澳門做「叠碼仔」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n捐款50萬元的英皇集團（0163）主要股東楊受成，1981年因介入騎師告東尼傷人案，被判妨礙司法公正罪成，入獄9個月；出獄後再於1998年捲入懷疑內幕交易案，罪成判罰1,000萬元，及禁止出任上市公司董事兩年。"},{"pid":"29fbc178fce577b3fc3922e63f68d68807ba137f","tid":144218,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T21:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"404cf77162aa1e8bce95972664043236beab9342","tid":144218,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"得人恩果千年記"},{"pid":"04d660e6b46f2507fb8a2a2c95bede3fdfce24fa","tid":144218,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"安家費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232028501ed92b788e23d24ca87917d35fefba25","tid":144218,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}